      "text": "琴乃、どうしたんだ？\nリハーサルでも調子がよくなさそうだったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ what’s the matter?\nYou didn’t seem in top form during rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.266666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
