    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……実は、その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}… To be honest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも言ってくれ\n本番前に気になることは解決しておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Go ahead. You can tell me anything.\nLet’s resolve this before the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 18.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今更なんですけど……\nやっぱりこんな格好で人前に出るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know it’s a bit late for this…\nBut going out in front of people‚ dressed like this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "も、もの凄く、恥ずかしいというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "i-is actually really embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.433333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "歌も動きもキレがなかったのはそれが原因か\n気恥ずかしい気持ちは分からないでもないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That explains the hesitancy in your singing and dancing.\nI can understand where you’re coming from‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーである琴乃がそんな風だと\nみんなもいつもの力を発揮出来なくなってしまうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you’re the leader‚ Kotono.\nThe others need you to set an example.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、私のせいで月ストのみんなに\n迷惑はかけられないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I don’t want to cause any trouble\nfor the other members of Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
